Package: PhotomossR
Type: Package
Title: Calculates Spectral Indices for Multiple Areas per Photo
Version: 1.1
Date: 2023-01-16
Author: Manuel Molina-Bustamante with essential collaboration from Indradatta deCastro-Arrazola
Maintainer: Manuel Molina-Bustamante <manuel.molinab@uam.es>
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Manuel", family = "Molina-Bustamante", email = "manuel.molinab@uam.es", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1057-6831"), role = c("aut", "cre")),
