Description: Calculates spectral vegetation and color indices (NDVI...) in multiple
    VIS (=VISible) and NIR (=Near InfraRed) pairs of photos. The package is 
    heavily based on package crustcover (available at GitHub username mosscoder).
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: raster
Imports: dplyr, rgeos, data.table, tiff, jpeg, sp, RColorBrewer, spatstat, RImageJROI
BugReports: https://github.com/MMolBus/PhotomossR/issues
